<figureCitation box="[160,224,1019,1045]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1752,1776]" captionTargetBox="[155,1432,417,1729]" captionTargetId="figure-96@2.[155,1432,417,1729]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Macroteratura (Macroteratura) inospina Chen, Cui &amp; Chang sp. nov., male: A–B. pronotum: A. lateral view; B. dorsal view; C–F. apex of abdomen: C. dorsal view; D. ventral view; E. lateral view; F. subgenital plate in ventral view; female: G. ovipositor in lateral view; H. subgenital plate in ventral view; g. distal half of genitalia; p. spine-like process of cercus apex on ventral surface." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4411615" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4411615/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="96">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
